            <para>All taxon groups recorded since 14/02/2017 and records of any data entered since 14/02/2017. Verified records from MBRP partners, including Manx Wildlife Trust, Manx Basking Shark Watch, BSBI, Isle of Man Flora Group and Isle of Man Fungus Group.
